{"type": "article", "id": 15861, "title": "Horizons积木", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-10T07:51:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125738780DCfwYVXK4JLjm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t玩积木和七巧板似乎是童年的事，这些木质积木能拼出假山和房屋建筑群的样子。来自西班牙的年轻设计师 Carlos Jiménez从木工房的边角料里获得灵感，将经过细心计算的三角形和四边形组成了12块的套装积木，它们随意变化，搭建出小型景观，是改变办公室枯燥环境的点缀。在摆弄当中，也能舒缓压力。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143147vrAnyZks31mMOIX5.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261431474eqmLNTac9wAKobz.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143148DlwKFPiHW49Vsqnh.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143148enAl7pJGgK0swqvI.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"656\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}